      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, what do you mean by \"startled goblin\"? lol. anyway, what about the bus part? if i have to take a local bus once i get to edinburgh to get to my hotel, should i worry about timing that too? i dont want to be stuck standing around in the rain if i miss a connection.",
